, \"to\": 1296}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just do not particularly know right now where to push those frustrations and where they should sit.\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1447, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those frustrations\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not think these are bad people.\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bad people\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am standing with the people that I signed with.\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1536, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that they are good people.\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good people\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think this is just a horrible situation.'\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1615, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a horrible situation\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Neita echoed Kerr's sentiments, telling BBC Sport.\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1657, \"end\": 1666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999997613631706, \"rank\": 2.3153010688652625e-07, \"text\": \"BBC Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Neita\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1622}, {\"ngram\": \"Kerr's sentiments\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Even one penny being owed is a significant amount,' she said.\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1730, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Even one penny\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1683}, {\"ngram\": \"a significant amount\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's kind of crazy.\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1751, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I sometimes think, \\\"I really want my money\\\".\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1796, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my money\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An athlete deserves what they are promised.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An athlete\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1807}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But you know, unfortunately, the league itself and Michael Johnson, ran into trouble.\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1894, \"end\": 1909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"score\": 0.6562406956374156, \"rank\": 0.2753288987434648, \"text\": \"Michael Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the league\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1882}, {\"ngram\": \"trouble\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know the full ins and outs of exactly what happened, but I would like to believe that it wasn't with ill intent, and it was a league that was started up with the best interest of the athletes.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 2130, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the full ins\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1955}, {\"ngram\": \"outs\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1964}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1980}, {\"ngram\": \"ill intent\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2049}, {\"ngram\": \"a league\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2070}, {\"ngram\": \"the best interest\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2113}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I would not want it to be like, \\\"Michael Johnson was a bad man.\\\"\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2166, \"end\": 2181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"score\": 0.6562406956374156, \"rank\": 0.2753288987434648, \"text\": \"Michael Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bad man\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2195}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not even think that's what it is.\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2236, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's one of the most respected athletes in the world, especially in our sport.\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2315, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most respected athletes\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2276}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2289}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2314}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's not looking likely that the athletes will be paid.\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2373, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am someone that got injured in the league.\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2386}, {\"ngram\": \"the league\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That affected my season... not putting the blame on anyone.\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2478, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my season\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2442}, {\"ngram\": \"the blame\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2467}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if it's physically not there, what can we do?'\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2529, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson vowed to 'save' track athletics when he launched his league in 2024, with the promise of lucrative prizes and elite billing.\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2663, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2531, \"end\": 2538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"score\": 0.9999994032234061, \"rank\": 5.763211700380132e-07, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"track athletics\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2570}, {\"ngram\": \"his league\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2598}, {\"ngram\": \"the promise\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2624}, {\"ngram\": \"lucrative prizes\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2644}, {\"ngram\": \"elite billing\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, a key backer withdrew after the first event in Jamaica in 2024 and the plan quickly unravelled, with GST filing for bankruptcy at the end of 2025.\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2720, \"end\": 2727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999999886313, \"rank\": 1.1208095443831307e-11, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 2774, \"end\": 2777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sales_tax\", \"score\": 0.591748607983428, \"rank\": 0.6899068058781421, \"text\": \"GST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sales_tax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sales_tax\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a key backer\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2685}, {\"ngram\": \"the first event\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2716}, {\"ngram\": \"the plan\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2748}, {\"ngram\": \"bankruptcy\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2799}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It incurred estimated liabilities of between \\u00a37.4million ($10m) and \\u00a337.4m ($50m) to more than 200 creditors.\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2929, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"estimated liabilities\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2853}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 200 creditors\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 2928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement last August, Johnson said: 'It is incredibly difficult to live with the reality that you have built something bigger than yourself while simultaneously feeling like you have let down the very people you set out to help.\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 3165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2959, \"end\": 2966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"score\": 0.9999994032234061, \"rank\": 5.763211700380132e-07, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2945}, {\"ngram\": \"the reality\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3025}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3055}, {\"ngram\": \"the very people\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We promised that athletes would be fairly and quickly compensated.\", \"from\": 3167, \"to\": 3234, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet, here we are struggling with our ability to compensate them.'\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3300, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our ability\", \"from\": 3268, \"to\": 3279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson clarified that it was his decision not to continue with the BBC after the Paris 2024 Games.\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3302, \"end\": 3309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"score\": 0.9999994032234061, \"rank\": 5.763211700380132e-07, \